OL,3,CShop price inflation eases to lowest
OL,4,Crate since December 2021
OL,6,FShop price inflation eased to its
OL,7,Flowest rate since December 2021 driven
OL,8,Fby falling food costs and competition
OL,9,Fbetween retailers, figures show.
OL,11,FShop prices were 1.3% higher than a
OL,12,Fyear ago in March, slowing from
OL,13,FFebruary's 2.5% and well below the
OL,14,Fthree-month average of 2.2%, according
OL,15,Fto the British Retail Consortium (BRC)-
OL,16,FNielsenIQ Shop Price Index.
