OL,3,CShop price inflation eases to lowest
OL,4,Crate since December 2021
OL,6,FFood prices overall were 3.7% higher
OL,7,Fthan a year ago, down from 5% in
OL,8,FFebruary, the 10th consecutive month
OL,9,Fof slowing inflation for the category
OL,10,Fand its lowest since April 2022.
OL,12,FFresh food inflation slowed further to
OL,13,F2.6% from 3.4% a month earlier.
OL,15,FInflation on products other than food
OL,16,Ffell to 0.2% in March, down from 1.3%
OL,17,Fin February, and its lowest since
OL,18,FJanuary 2022.
