OL,3,CShop price inflation eases to lowest
OL,4,Crate since December 2021
OL,6,FBRC chief executive Helen Dickinson
OL,7,Fsaid: "While Easter treats were more
OL,8,Fexpensive than in previous years due
OL,9,Fto high global cocoa and sugar prices,
OL,10,Fretailers provided cracking deals on
OL,11,Fpopular chocolates, which led to price
OL,12,Ffalls compared to the previous month.
OL,14,F"Dairy prices also fell on the month
OL,15,Fas farmgate prices eased, and
OL,16,Fretailers worked hard to lower prices
OL,17,Ffor many essentials.
