OL,3,CShop price inflation eases to lowest
OL,4,Crate since December 2021
OL,6,F"In non-food, prices of electricals,
OL,7,Fclothing and footwear fell as
OL,8,Fretailers increased promotions to
OL,9,Fentice consumer spending."
OL,11,FMike Watkins, head of retailer and
OL,12,Fbusiness insight at NielsenIQ, said:
OL,13,F"The slowdown in inflation continues
OL,14,Fand a key driver this month was a
OL,15,Ffurther fall in food prices.
OL,17,F"A year ago, food inflation was 15% so
OL,18,Fthis was to be expected.
